Text: Thankyou so much, you are fabulous!!
Love your work, as per usual Gaz!
Gemma sends you her love and kisses Gary.
I saw Gemma on 8 out of 10 cats! That was one of the funniest things I have seen in a long long time!!!
Hey Gary whats up. I'm still in California hiding the fact that I watch this shit knowing full well that if my friends find out their gonna beat my ass for my own good.

Good to hear you're still alive mate! You know, I tried watching an episode of TOWIE from the start and one of the more recent ones and it did nothing for me. I enjoy it when it is broken down for 8 out of 10 Cats's jokes!!
One of the bits they showed on 8 out of 10 was from the season 5 finale, Gary, in case you need to see more of Gemma in her swimsuit.
